pageContext.claim: “Few, if any, Administrations have done more in just 7 months than the Trump A. Bills passed, regulations killed, border, military, ISIS, SC!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump, unlike many presidents in their 7th month, has signed no major legislation. at the time of the tweet, he had signed 55 bills, most of which were minor. Just among recent presidents, Jimmy Carter, George H.W. Bush and Bill Clinton had signed more bills than Trump at this point in their presidencies.
